DocConstant.Name: TOPSOILREMOVAL
DocConstant.Documentation: Excavation where the topmost layer of soil containing organic material is cut or stripped. The removed topsoil can be used as fill ([<font color="#0000ff"><u>EarthworksElement</u></font>]($element://{04D59E49-786C-4558-8F2F-4AC00545AE17})) e.g. where planting is planned.
